<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-title>Vérifyé imél a-w</mj-title>
    <mj-font name="Noto Serif" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Noto+Serif" />
    <mj-font name="Titillium Web" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Titillium+Web:400,600" />
    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-class name="title" font-family="Titillium Web" font-weight="600" font-size="20px" />
      <mj-class name="code" font-family="Titillium Web" font-weight="400" font-size="12px" />
      <mj-all font-family="Noto Serif" font-size="13px" line-height="17px" />
    </mj-attributes>
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body background-color="#ccd3e0">
    <!-- header -->
    <mj-section background-color="#422B8F">
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#fff" padding-bottom="20px" padding-top="20px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text mj-class="title">
          {{user.firstname}}, ou obliyé modpas a-w ?
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
        <p>
Nou ka voyé lyen-lasa davwa ou pa ka sonjé ki modpas ou té mèt lèwvwè ou té enskri-w asi Kreyolopal.
        </p>
        <p>
        Si a pa vou ki mandé-sa, pa okipé-w dè mésaj-lasa. Si sé vou, pijé si bouton-la pou mèt ondòt modpas.
        </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button background-color="#422B8F" href="{{confirm_url}}">Chanjé modpas</mj-button>
        <mj-text>
          Si bouton-la pa ka maché, ou ké ni a kopyé lyen-lasa :
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class="code">
          {{confirm_url}}
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#f7f7fc">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-social>
          <mj-social-element href="#" name="facebook" />
          <mj-social-element href="#" name="twitter" />
        </mj-social>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#141414">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text color="#e7e7e7" align="center" font-size="9px">
          &copy; Plume Magique 2020
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

  </mj-body>
</mjml>